\id 2PE 2PE - Bible Iyansi 
\h 2 PETƆLÀ 
\toc1 Un'kaan wàyweel wà Petɔlà 
\toc2 2 PETƆLÀ 
\toc3 2Pe 
\mt2 Un'kaan wàyweel wà 
\mt1 Petɔlà 
\imt1 Nsɛmà 
\ip Un'kaan a Petɔlà wàyweel bàtöm anki itàkal akà Ikööŋ a bul làmwɛy, itàkal naa akundweer a isal mwɛy, itàkal naa akaklistɔ bàpää u mɛɛn. Waa wun'kaan a un'sɛŋ anà waa sye wasànaa kyän a dweelà. Ndaa a ngwal awa yà ntɔn munwaan a baar bàfiipay ngyɛb an'lɔŋ a nsöön a Làsaŋ, làsaŋ aŋàbwaŋ là Nzam. Ndaa a mfun Ungö a mbɔr a nsɛmà, indiir itär bye muyilääb. Wàntàtɛr wàmuŋyɛm unsà ndaa iler làbɔ̈ɔ̈n bàwɛl akà Nzam anà unsà imbäl a baar abà bàmɛn Mwol. Wàyweel mutɔn a ngwal isal a alɔɔŋ a loor bàfàkwaar mbwo a ndaa ndandaa anà yà balàbal. Wàtär utɔn ndaa mwɛy unsà ntɛn a ba: ba bàfàtɛn naa ngyeel a Klistɔ isàkal anki. Petɔlà kàfuur naa isàkal naa ya yan'kyer itaan, yàntɔn nkääŋàmpem a Nzam. Mbɔr a ntsü yàmupà un'kanà anà ngwal akà baar awà bàtöm waa anà akun'tääŋ a un'kaan awà wanswà. Mɛɛn màkɔ̈ɔ̈n anki akà ikikye anà baar bàfàkɔ̈ɔ̈n a kwaar Làsaŋ. Un'kaan a Petɔlà wàyweel wà un'kaan a ndaa: waa wàmupà un'kanà akà aklistɔ mukyà usà unsà ngyööb a Mwol, ntɔn mukɔɔn a tɔɔmà ndwaŋ umbwo a an'lɔŋ aŋàtà mbeen anà màbɔɔmà. Asöön itàkal atääŋ a biblɛ bamwɛy bàfàtɛn naa un'kaan awà wà ntööm Petɔlà kusà a ukwà nde u mbul wà an'kwem an'syaam aŋinà ungö a Yɛsu Klistɔ. Itàkal naa abà, undiir kan'söön uboo awa, yà ngyeel a Mwol. Ngö a nsööŋ a ngyeel a Mwol ayi, wà undiir mwɛy akà baar mpa abà Ayudà anà aklistɔ binkye mubɛy ya. Abun, un'kaan wàmuyɔɔb naa ngö a nsöŋ umii a Mwol kà ndaa a ngwal anki, wɛɛ nkääŋ a mpem ande ayà yaay bàpɛ akà baar banswà ntɔn muwal mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà musɔɔm nkääl. Un'kaan awà, wàmusà an'kyän unsà in'kaan a Nkwà itaan asànaa Nkwà akün. Abà yàkäl ndaa a ngywoolà a ntabwey a Mwol, amu ya Petɔlà wàŋàtà din. 
\ie  
\c 1  
\s1 Mbɔr 
\p  
\v 1 Mɛ Simɔn Petɔlà, un'syääl anà ntööm a Yɛsu Klistɔ. 
\p An'söön baar abà bàwɛl làkwikilà aŋàbwaŋ asànaa bi unsà balàbal a Nzam abi anà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ Yɛsu Klistɔ.  
\v 2 Wɛy kab a ngway anà duu màkäl mbɔɔn anà bɛ, u mbwo a ngyööb a Nzam anà Yɛsu, Mwol abi! 
\s1 Làbeel anà nsɔ̈ɔ̈l a Nzam 
\p  
\v 3 Abun, ngwal a du yipɛ kab aya yanswà yà ndöŋ ntɔn mɔ̈ɔ̈ anà inzaam, ntɔn bi iyöb mbuur kibel unsà làkoo ande ŋakwo anà ngwal ifàsal.  
\v 4 Kyakin, bi kàwɛl an'kab a ntal akölàköl amà bipɛ ilää, ntɔn, u mbwo a ma, bɛ làwɛl kab unsà inzaam, bɛ baar bàlagyɔɔr unsà làbiin ufàdii ilään a mɛɛn. 
\p  
\v 5 Kyakin, làsi ngwal abɛ yanswà mukwɛy làkwikilà unsà nkääl aŋàbwaŋ, unsà nkääl aŋàbwaŋ, làsi ngyööb,  
\v 6 unsà ngyööb, nkääŋ a mpem, unsà nkääŋ a mpem, imbämdir, unsà imbämdir, inzaam,  
\v 7 unsà inzaam, un'tüüb a atɔŋ a atɔŋ, unsà un'tüüb a atɔŋ a atɔŋ, ukwen.  
\v 8 Ntɔn, isàkal naa bɛ làbye anà nkääl ayi yàmbɔɔn, ya iyàlasiinà musal anà muyɛl unsà ngyööb a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ.  
\v 9 Wɛɛ akà mbuur akɔ̈ɔ̈n bya, nde wà ikwàmii, nde akyer afàbàba: nde uyöb anki naa nde wàŋàpɔŋà unsà man'be ande mà itaan. 
\p  
\v 10 Kyakin, atɔŋ, fàlasye ngwal ntɔn mutà làbeel abɛ mpi anà nsɔ̈ɔ̈l abɛ. Abun, waa bɔɔmà abwà mpa bàkal akà ikikye.  
\v 11 Kyakin, waa mbiilà abɛ unsà Imwol a mbul a in'tye kyà Mwol anà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi Yɛsu Klistɔ isàkal yàŋàduub kölàköl. 
\p  
\v 12 Kyakin, mɛ in'wɛy anki mufàlayɔɔb indiir abi, itàkal naa bɛ bya làkyàyöb anà bɛ làbà aŋàtsim unsà ndandaa ayà bàlapɛ.  
\v 13 Wɛɛ mɛ in'sii naa yàbalàbal muwiy an'kyän abɛ u mbwo a ngyɔɔb amɛ umpal in'wà mɛ uboo a ipfey a ndür ki.  
\v 14 Ntɔn mɛ in'kyàyöb naa taaŋ muwɛy ipfey a ndür aki làmuyà u ntiin, asànaa kan'swɛŋ Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ.  
\v 15 Wɛɛ mɛ, mɛ in'sàsà ngwal naa ungö a nkyeen amɛ, bɛ làyɔbà an'lɔɔŋ amà taaŋ lanswà. 
\s1 Ndaa a aŋangɔɔm yan'kwo amu Klistɔ 
\p  
\v 16 Abun, kà ntɔn mulab nsim a ntwan anki waa bi kàlakyään ngyeel a Mwol abi Yɛsu Klistɔ unsà ngwal ande yanswà, wɛɛ ntɔn kàmɛn bi uteer ande u mii abi ŋakwo!  
\v 17 Ntɔn nde kàwɛl ibyääl anà làkoo akà Taa Nzam, umpal kàtɛn nde a nde unsà làkoo ande làkölàköl naa: « Wà, wà mwaan amɛ wànkwen, awà kàsi mɛ un'sak amɛ amu nde. »  
\v 18 Ndaa ayi yàfü du, bi ŋakwo kàkyer awem ya, umpal kàkäl bi anà nde u mɔŋ in'kyɛɛl. 
\p  
\v 19 Abun, bi ibye anà ndaa a bwoor yàŋangɔɔm. Bɛ làkäl anà iböŋ musà mii abɛ udu aya asànaa mwin afàlɛɛmà kà ikal a làpib, tii umpal làyaanà taaŋ anà uyàsɛnà mbwaar a tutu uboo a mpem abɛ.  
\v 20 Kusà aya yanswà, làyöb abà: akà mbuur mwɛy ukwe anki nde ŋakwo mutà itàkal mubaal ngɔɔm ayà uboo a Ndaa Aŋàsɔn.  
\v 21 Kyakin, ngɔɔm kà ifàfà anki akà ikikye unsà ukwen a mbuur, wɛɛ unsà ngwal a Dweelà In'kyɛɛl waa baar bàyäm kà ikↄb a Nzam. 
\c 2  
\s1 Alɔɔŋ a loor 
\r (Yud 4-13) 
\p  
\v 1 Asànaa bàkäl aŋangɔɔm a loor uboo a un'sɛŋ a Isàlɛl, abun sye, bàsàkal alɔɔŋ a loor uboo a bɛ. Ba bàsàbiil an'lɔɔŋ an'be a ntwan, tii mutɔn Un'lɔɔŋ awà katsü mɔ̈ɔ̈. Kwɛl a mbɔɔn tɛy, ma màsabwiy ndwaŋ.  
\v 2 Baar mbɔɔn bàsàlab mbweel a ndwaŋ aba. Ntɔn ba, mbwo a ndandaa isàbulà undiir mwɛy wàŋàbɛy.  
\v 3 Unsà küüb a ngim, alɔɔŋ a loor abà bàsàwal indiir abɛ u mbwo ndaa a ntsà. Wɛɛ ntɔn ba, fà itaan, ntaaŋàmbar aba kwɛl yatɛy anà ukwà aba bàyàfàdil anki. 
\p  
\v 4 Ntɔn, Nzam kàwɛy anki akyeey bàkyer man'be, wɛɛ nde katɔɔm u nsye a mbaa, bàŋàbäm an'dwaaŋ ntɔn mudil mbar.  
\v 5 Nde sye kàwɛy anki taaŋ là itaan, wɛɛ nde kàyee Nɔwà, mbuur wànaan uboo a baar bàsɔrà unsà ukwà, nde mbuur kàlɔɔŋà balàbal umpal kàdwä Nzam baar abe kà an'dà umpal kànɔ̈ mbul a ikül.  
\v 6 Ungö apan, nde kàpɛ ntaaŋàmbar akà an'bul a Sɔdɔm anà Gɔmɔr anà ma mabulà un'twà ntɔn muswaŋ mbaan akà baar abe abà bàsàyà ungö.  
\v 7 Wɛɛ nde kàtsü Lɔt mɔ̈ɔ̈, mbuur a balàbal awà kàwem ngyɛb ntɔn isal aŋingyäy byà atɔŋ ande.  
\v 8 Ntɔn mbuur a balàbal awà kàkäl umwɛy uboo a ba, nde kàkyer amanà anà kàkyer awemà: ilä ungö ilä, mpem ande yàkyer ayɔɔ ntɔn isal aba byà ŋingyäy.  
\v 9 Abun, Mwol an'kwo ulwom u nsii baar a balàbal anà usi ukɔl baar mpa abà bàbalàbal ntɔn mukapà ntaaŋàmbar kà ilä a nsaŋ.  
\v 10 Ntaaŋàmbar ayi yà sin sin ntɔn baar bàfàkwen ŋingyäy. Ba bàfàlab ilään a ndür aba anà bàfàbɛy ikɔ̈b a Nzam. 
\p Alɔɔŋ a loor abà bye anà gyɔɔr anà uyɔl, bɔɔmà akà ba batɛy mubweel baar a làkoo a du in'tswe.  
\v 11 Itàkal akyeey ban'lyaaŋ ikɔ̈b anà ngwal udu a ba, bàfàtɛn anki ndaa a nswɛn akà ba u mii a Mwol.  
\v 12 Wɛɛ ba bà asànaa ntsür a insil ifàkwɛlà anà ifàkwà unsà intaam. Ba bàfàto indiir mpa bàyöb ba. Ba bàkyer asàpɔɔn asànaa ufàpɔɔn ntsür.  
\v 13 Abà, ba bàsàwal làfur a un'kɔl aŋàyↄŋ aba. Un'sak aba wàmukyer ndaa a nswɛn kà imɛɛy.  
\v 14 Mii aba myàŋàyɔl a inswem, ba bàfàyuur anki mukyer man'be, ba bàfàlwab baar mpa abàŋàtsim. Ba bàkyàtoo làpaan a ngyal a ngim. Un'küül a Nzam wà udu a ba!  
\v 15 Ba ban'wɛy mbwo a swalaa, ba ban'yiiŋ ntɔn mulab mbwo a Bàlam mwan a Bɔsɔr, awà kàbü unsà ndɛb a làfur làkɔ̈ɔ̈n balàbal,  
\v 16 wɛɛ nde kàwɛl làfur a un'tswe bwoor ande: ntsür a nkiin mwɛy wà isal kàsi ndaa asànaa mbuur, abun, ukɔŋ a ŋangɔɔm awà waa bàwü. 
\p  
\v 17 Baar abà bà asànaa ntwà mpa ifàtwey an'dà anà an'tööb ufiisyen un'pöb. Ba bàkyalɔ̈ɔ̈n ikal u diŋàdiŋ a mpib.  
\v 18 Abun, unsà an'lɔɔŋ aba màŋàyam a uyɔl anà màbunàbun, ba bàfàlwab baar ban'sɔrà benàben kà an'kɔɔ a baar abye anà mɔ̈ɔ̈ un'be.  
\v 19 Ba bàfasyeel ilää ntɔn mukapà insaay, wɛɛ, kyekà ba ŋakwo bà asɔ a ilään ifatwääl ukwà, ntɔn mbuur wanswà wà un'sɔ a undiir awà afun'yaal.  
\v 20 Abun, isàkal naa baar bàsɔrà kà an'kɔɔ a mbiin a mɛɛn u mbwo a ngyööb a Yɛsu Klistɔ, Mwol anà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi, ban'fàbwà anà bàmàfayaal unsà mbiin a mɛɛn, mpay aba yàngöngö yan'söön yàtàtwɛb.  
\v 21 Ntɔn yàlàkal ubwaŋ akà ba mukɔɔn ayöb mbwo a balàbal, wɛɛ kàmuyöb ya anki, waa ungö bàfàtɔn nswɛɛŋ a in'kyɛɛl ayà bàtöm.  
\v 22 Ya yayeel asànaa kyàtɛn itim asànaa ayà ya: « Mbwà kan'fàfurà kà ilwo ande » naa sye: « Ngul un'kyay bàmun'ywɛy làbenàben, kan'fàbibimà uboo a antwar. » 
\c 3  
\s1 Ilää a ngyeel a Mwol 
\p  
\v 1 Asam amɛ, wà wun'kaan wàyweel alàsöön mɛ. Uboo a mya myemyeel, mɛ an'lɔm akà ngyɔɔb abɛ ntɔn muwiy amu bɛ nsyääl a balàbal muyweer.  
\v 2 Làyɔbà ndaa bàtɛn aŋangɔɔm in'kyɛɛl kusà anà nswɛɛŋ a antööm abɛ, nswɛɛŋ a Mwol anà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈.  
\v 3 Làyöb kusà naa: kà ilä a ntsüü, baar a nkääl ambe bàsàkyer ayà, waa bàsàlasɛ,  
\v 4 bàsàtɛn naa: « Kyàken ilä a ngyeel ande? Ntɔn, fà bàkü ataa, akà nsɔɔmà mwɛy yi yatɛy. Ndaa yanswà yà ifà imwɛy fà bàkyer mɛɛn! »  
\v 5 Unsà ntɛɛn aba ayi, ba ban'diimà naa fà itaan itaan, làkäl anà du. Anà mɛɛn màtoo unsà an'dà, ma mà uboboo a an'dà unsà ngwal a Nzam.  
\v 6 U mbwo a ma sye, mɛɛn mà itaan màminà uboo a an'dà.  
\v 7 Unsà ndaa iler du anà mɛɛn a ŋàbà, Ndaa nsil ya yàmadil ntɔn mbaa, kà ilä a nsaŋ, anà ukwà a baar abe. 
\p  
\v 8 Asam amɛ bànkwen, we anà undiir mwɛy mpa lan'kwo bɛ mukyäärà mpiim: ntɔn akà Mwol, ilä mwɛy kyà asànaa nsaab mwɛy yà mbul, anà nsaab mwɛy yà mbul yà sànaa ilä mwɛy.  
\v 9 Akà Mwol ngö a nsöŋ yatɛy mukwey ilää ande, asànaa bàfàsii bamwɛy naa nde asàkyer itaan, wɛɛ nde we anà nkääŋ a mpem ntɔn bɛ, ntɔn nde ukwen anki naa bamwɛy bàkü, wɛɛ, naa baar banswà bàbuul mpem aba.  
\v 10 Wɛɛ ilä a Mwol isàyà asànaa mbüüb. Ilä làsàdubà du, làso làsàkal làkölàköl, indiir aŋàbääb ikyer asàkaabà, mɛɛn anà isal ama màsàkal u nsaŋ.  
\v 11 Mpal isàpää indiir abi byanswà, bɛ làsàkal baar a nkye ifà! Mɔ̈ɔ̈ in'kyɛɛl nà! Làzir nà akà Nzam!  
\v 12 Bɛ, bɛ baar làkadilà anà làkanaanà ngyeel a ilä a Nzam, ilä làsàyaalà du aŋàkuŋà anà indiir aŋàbääb ikyer asàyaalà!  
\v 13 Bi ibà mudilà du akün anà mɛɛn akün asànaa akyà ilää ande, ikal làbà bàbalàbal.  
\v 14 Kyakin, asam amɛ, unsà ndiil ayi, làkyer ngwal ntɔn nde kàlamɛn unsà duu aŋàkwo anà làkɔ̈ɔ̈n an'pɛl.  
\v 15 Anà làyöb ubwaŋàbwaŋ naa nkääŋ a mpem a kölàköl a Mwol, yà ntɔn mɔ̈ɔ̈ abɛ! Yà unsà an'kyän amà, waa Pɔl, un'tɔŋ anà un'sam abi, kàmàlasöön asànaa amà an'yeerà kun'pɛ Nzam.  
\v 16 Ndaa ayi nde ya kan'tɛn sye unsà in'kaan myanswà kàsön nde: Ye anà ndaa yumwɛy yà bwoor muyöb uboo a in'kaan ami, insil anà baar bàkɔ̈ɔ̈n un'yɛnà la bàfakwaar ba an'kyän a mya, asànaa bàfàkwaar ba an'kyän a In'kaan myumwɛy ntɔn ba ŋakwo bàbü ndwaŋ.  
\v 17 Wɛɛ bɛ, ankwen amɛ, asànaa lan'yöb bɛ kusà, làkäl unsà igyɛɛŋ, twon lan'lab abɛɛy abà bàfàdiimà mbwo anà twon lan'piy làkyän abɛ!  
\v 18 Wɛɛ làyɛl unsà kab angway anà ngyööb a Mwol anà Un'tswää a mɔ̈ɔ̈ abi Yɛsu Klistɔ. Wɛy làkoo làkäl akà nde fà ŋàbà tii mbul a in'tye. Wöö wöö.